::Decadel::

	Decadel comes toward Paralysis, carefully, making sure he doesn't all of a
sudden open fire.  Decadel steps inside the base, and looks around.  

	"Hello.  My name is Decadel.  I'm glad you let me join your faction!  I
have one question to ask you, do you by any chance know what this symbol
represents?" Decadel said, showing Paralysis the Predacon symbols on his
shoulders.
